== The cron job

Executed every hour on :04 and :34, errors are logged.

TRAKKOR_PATH=/home/mat/www/trakkor
04,34 * * * * /usr/local/bin/ruby $TRAKKOR_PATH/fetch-n-save.rb >> $TRAKKOR_PATH/log/cron.log 2>&1

New variable in 
/etc/environment
must be named:
TRAKKOR_PATH=/home/mat/repos/git/trakkor

